structure.unit: A JUSTICE AND PUBLIC SAFETY CABINET

law.history: Repealed 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 334, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 343, sec. 8, effective July 15, 1982; and ch. 377, sec. 6, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. V, sec. 14.
